---
import Pretext from "./Pretext.astro";
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="section-padding bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900/50"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative">
    {/* Decorative background element */}
    <div class="absolute -top-24 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <Pretext text="Strategic Foundation" />
      
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold mb-12 text-balance leading-[1.1]">
        Bridging the gap between <span class="italic">Analytics</span> and Code.
      </h2>
      
      <div
        class="space-y-10 text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light"
      >
        <p>
          With a Master's in Data Science, I bridge the critical gap between
          raw technical data modeling and strategic product management. My
          core specialization lies in <span class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white font-medium italic">unit economics</span>—specifically focusing on
          LTV:CAC optimization.
        </p>
        <p>
          My foundational experience spans across the OTT and tech landscapes
          in India, where I've successfully designed monetization frameworks
          and built market-entry strategies for heavy vertical-specific SaaS
          applications.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-900 dark:text-white font-serif italic text-2xl md:text-3xl mt-12">
          "I believe that engineered products must be commercially viable."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-12 md:gap-24 mt-20">
        <div class="group">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">MS</div>
          <div
            class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500 mt-4 font-bold"
          >
            Data Science
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-px h-20 bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-neutral-800 hidden md:block"></div>
        <div class="group">
          <div class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">100%</div>
          <div
            class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500 mt-4 font-bold"
          >
            Data Focused
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
